<span rend="jisage_1" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 1em">かず／＼並ニ</span>
<span rend="jisage_1" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 1em">おはなし</span>
長き御返じ<lb />
<span rend="jisage_1" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 1em">被<span rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</span>下度候。</span>
